songs.title: He Made Me Do It
songs.lyrics:
[Pre-Chorus]
That's enough, had enough, sick of this drama
Temperature is high and it's finna get hotter
That's enough, had enough, sick of this drama
Temperature is high and it's finna get hotter
That's enough, had enough, sick of this drama
Temperature is high and it's finna get hotter

[Chorus]
My mind is going to explode
If I don't get some self control
Not my fault, the Devil made me do it
Yo, you know the Devil? Yeah, he made me do it
I feel him deep within my soul
It makes me lose my self control
Not my fault, the Devil made me do it
Yo, you know the Devil? Yeah, he made me do it
